data.title: ESEA Season 31: Advanced Division - Europe
data.meta_description: ESEA Season 31: Advanced Division - Europe is an online European CS:GO tournament organized by ESEA. This C-Tier tournament took place from Apr 29 to Jul 17 2019 featuring 70 teams competing over a total prize pool of $15,000 USD.
